  padding: 10px 20px 10px 15px;
  position: relative;
  text-decoration: none
}

.button-custom:hover {
  background: #eee
}

.button-custom,
.button-custom:after,
.button-custom:before {
  -moz-transform-style: preserve-3d;
  -moz-transition: -moz-transform 0.75s, background-color .125s;
  -ms-transform-style: preserve-3d;
  -ms-transition: -ms-transform 0.75s, background-color .125s;
  -webkit-transform-style: preserve-3d;
  -webkit-transition: -webkit-transform 0.75s, background-color .125s;
  transform-style: preserve-3d;
  transition: transform 0.75s, background-color .125s
}

.button-custom:after,
.button-custom:before {
  -moz-backface-visibility: hidden;
  -ms-backface-visibility: hidden;
  -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
  backface-visibility: hidden;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  position: absolute;
  right: 0;
  top: 0
}

.button-custom:before {
  z-index: 2
}

.button-custom i.ic-geo {
  background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
  background-position: left center;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  float: left;
  height: 18px;
  margin: -3px 2px 0;
  width: 18px
}

.button-custom:after {
  -moz-border-radius: 5px;
  -moz-transform: rotateX(180deg);
  -ms-transform: rotateX(180deg);
  -webkit-border-radius: 5px;
  -webkit-transform: rotateX(180deg);
  background-color: #999;
  background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);
  background-position: center center;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  border-color: #888;
  border-radius: 5px;
  content: '';
  transform: rotateX(180deg);
  z-index: 1
}

.button-custom.btn-loading {
  -moz-transform: rotateX(180deg);
  -ms-transform: rotateX(180deg);
  -webkit-transform: rotateX(180deg);
  transform: rotateX(180deg)
}

  border-radius: 3px;
  color: #FFF;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 2px 8px
}

.tuto-content+br,
.tuto-footer+br,
.tuto-header+br {
  display: none
}

.tuto-content,
.tuto-footer,
.tuto-header {
  border-spacing: 0;
  width: 100%
}

.tuto-header a,
.tuto-header font {
  color: #FFF!important
}

.tuto-header {
  background: #39C;
  border: 1px solid #39C;
  border-radius: 3px 3px 0 0;
  color: #FFF;
  font-family: "Trebuchet MS", Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, FontAwesome;
  padding: 3px
}

.tuto-logo,
.tuto-type {
  height: 75px;
  position: relative;
  text-align: center;
  width: 150px
}

.tuto-title {
  font-size: 22px;
  text-align: center
}

.tuto-logo:after {
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  content: "\f086";
  font-family: FontAwesome;
  font-size: 49px;
  font-style: normal;
  font-variant: normal;
  font-weight: normal;
  line-height: 1;
  text-rendering: auto
}

.announcement .tuto-logo:after {
  content: "\f0a1"
}

.tutorial .tuto-logo:after {
  content: "\f0d0"
}

.rules .tuto-logo:after {
  content: "\f071"
}

.review .tuto-logo:after {
  content: "\f046"
}

.graphic .tuto-logo:after {
  content: "\f1fc"
}

.tuto-type:after {
  background: #FFF;
  border-radius: 0 0 3px 3px;
  color: #39C;
  content: "Template";
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 3px 9px;
  position: absolute;
  right: 20px;
  top: -3px
}

.announcement .tuto-type:after {
  content: "Announcement"
}

.tutorial .tuto-type:after {
  color: #8B5;
  content: "Tutorial"
}

.rules .tuto-type:after {
  color: #787dea;
  content: "Important"
}

.review .tuto-type:after {
  color: #5AB584;
  content: "Review"
}

.graphic .tuto-type:after {
  color: #e06b59;
  content: "Graphic Design"
}

.tuto-content {
  background: #FFF;
  border: 1px solid #39C;
  border-bottom: 3px dashed #CCC!important;
  font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, FontAwesome;
  padding: 3px 20px
}

.tuto-footer {
  background: #FFF;
  border: 1px solid #39C;
  border-bottom-width: 5px;
  border-radius: 0 0 3px 3px;
  border-top: none
}

.tuto-credit {
  padding: 10px 6px;
  position: relative;
  text-align: justify;
  vertical-align: middle
}

.tuto-brand {
  height: 60px;
  padding: 6px 0;
  text-align: center;
  vertical-align: bottom;
  width: 120px
}

.tuto-brand:before {
  color: #39C;
  content: "Forum"
}

.tuto-brand:after {
  color: #333;
  content: "otion.com"
}

.tuto-credit:after {
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  bottom: 20px;
  color: #39C;
  content: "\f086";
  font-family: FontAwesome;
  font-size: 49px;
  font-style: normal;
  font-variant: normal;
  font-weight: normal;
  line-height: 1;
  position: absolute;
  right: -85px;
  text-rendering: auto
}

.postbody img[longdesc="213"],
.postbody img[longdesc="214"] {
  vertical-align: middle
}

table.list-in-tutos {
  border: 0;
  border-spacing: 0;
  width: 100%
}

table.list-in-tutos td {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #DDD;
  padding: 5px
}

.tuto-info-green {
  background-color: #b7e5a0;
  color: #000;
  width: 100%
}

.tuto-info-red {
  background-color: #E9553C;
  color: #fff;
  width: 100%
}

.tuto-header.tutorial {
  background-color: #8B5;
  border-color: #8B5
}

.tutorial+.tuto-content,
.tutorial+.tuto-content+.tuto-footer,
.tutorial+br+.tuto-content,
.tutorial+br+.tuto-content+br+.tuto-footer {
  border-color: #8B5
}

.tuto-header.rules {
  background-color: #787dea;
  border-color: #787dea
}

.rules+.tuto-content,
.rules+.tuto-content+.tuto-footer,
.rules+br+.tuto-content,
.rules+br+.tuto-content+br+.tuto-footer {
  border-color: #787dea
}

.tuto-header.review {
  background-color: #5AB584;
  border-color: #5AB584
}

.review+.tuto-content,
.review+.tuto-content+.tuto-footer,
.review+br+.tuto-content,
.review+br+.tuto-content+br+.tuto-footer {
  border-color: #5AB584
}

.sticker-points img,
.tuto-content table[style="width:100%;"] td[style="width:50%;text-align:center;"] img {
  vertical-align: middle
}

.tuto-header.graphic {
  background-color: #e06b59;
  border-color: #e06b59
}

.graphic+.tuto-content,
.graphic+.tuto-content+.tuto-footer,
.graphic+br+.tuto-content,
.graphic+br+.tuto-content+br+.tuto-footer {
  border-color: #e06b59
}

#cp-main .panel.sig::before,
#cp-main .panel.sig:before {
  background: #F5F5F5;
  border: 1px solid #DDD;
  border-bottom-width: 2px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  color: #E53;
  content: 'Attention : Your settings will be saved, however note, that only staff members can display signatures on the forum.';
  display: block;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin: 6px 0;
  padding: 6px;
  text-align: center
}


.sceditor-button-modcolor div {
  background-image: url(https://i.servimg.com/u/f56/18/45/41/65/mcolo10.png)!important
}

.sceditor-button-presets div {
  background-image: url(https://i.servimg.com/u/f39/18/21/41/30/tuto14.png)!important
}

div.sceditor-dropdown.sceditor-presets {
  padding: 0;
  width: 175px
}

.sceditor-presets .group {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #CCC;
  height: 150px;
  overflow-y: auto
}

.sceditor-presets a.toggler {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #CCC;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700
}

.sceditor-presets i {
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-right: 5px;
  text-align: center;
  width: 20px
}

.sceditor-presets img {
  margin-right: 5px;
  vertical-align: middle;
  width: 15px
}

.postbody .content,
.sceditor-container textarea {
  font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, FontAwesome!important
}


.post-button a {
  -webkit-transition: 300ms;
  background-color: #39C;
  border: 1px solid #39C;
  border-radius: 3px;
  color: #FFF;
  display: inline-block;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 6px 12px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: 300ms
}

.post-button.red a {
  background-color: #E53;
  border-color: #E53
}

.post-button.green a {
  background-color: #8C5;
  border-color: #8C5
}

.post-button.yellow a {
  background-color: #EB3;
  border-color: #EB3
}

.post-button a:hover {
  background-color: #28B
}

.post-button.red a:hover {
  background-color: #D42
}

.post-button.green a:hover {
  background-color: #7B4
}

.post-button.yellow a:hover {
  background-color: #DA2
}

.post-button a:active,
.post-button a:focus {
  background-color: #333!important;
  border-color: #222!important
}

.post-button i {
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: FontAwesome;
  font-size: inherit;
  font-style: normal;
  font-variant: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1;
  text-rendering: auto;
  transform: translate(0, 0)
}

.post div[style*="-30px;"] {
  top: -60px!important
}

#sticky_forum_options {
  left: 0;
  position: absolute
}

#sticky_forum_options a.mainmenu {
  padding: 0 6px
}

#sticky_forum_options i.fa {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 30px
}

a.fa_toggle {
  background: #FFF;
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: #39C;
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 10px;
  height: 20px;
  line-height: 20px;
  margin-top: -5px;
  position: absolute;
  text-align: center;
  width: 20px
}

.inline-code,
.inline-code * {
  display: inline-block!important
}

.inline-code code.prettyprint * {
  display: inline!important
}

.inline-code .codebox {
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04)!important;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  line-height: 12px;
  margin: 0
}

#mpage-body .inline-code .codebox p,
.inline-code .codebox dt {
  display: none!important
}

.inline-code .codebox code {
  margin-top: -3px
}

.sceditor-button-inline-code div {
  background-image: url(https://i.servimg.com/u/f21/18/21/41/30/snippe10.png)!important
}

.prettyprint ol.linenums {
  list-style-type: decimal!important
}

#recent_topic_list {
  font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  height: 250px;
  margin: -10px -10px -5px;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  overflow-y: auto;
  padding: 10px 3px 10px 10px
}

#recent_topic_list::-webkit-scrollbar {
  width: 6px
}

#recent_topic_list::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)
}

#recent_topic_list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: #39C
}

.topic_row {
  margin-bottom: 12px
}

.topic_row:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0
}

.module.mod_news .content table+br {
  display: none
}

#wrapper:after {
  clear: both;
  content: ".";
  display: block;
  height: 0;
  visibility: hidden
}

.post .postbody table dl.codebox code {
  word-break: break-all
}

#memberlist .avatar-mini+td {
  max-width: 250px;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  white-space: nowrap
}
